rows.label: qst701005_msg0001
rows.name: Heyyyy guys! What are you doing here?

rows.label: qst701005_msg0002
rows.name:
Here to explore the Divine Beast's neck too?
...Or not?

rows.label: qst701005_msg0003
rows.name:
As lovely as that sounds, there's
actually some stuff going on that
we wanted to discuss.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0004
rows.name: No need to be so cryptic Laura.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0005
rows.name:
Let's just cut to the chase. We need
your help, Rita.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0006
rows.name: Y-you need ME?

rows.label: qst701005_msg0007
rows.name:
Ooh, don't tell me... Is it some kind of
spicy food eating contest?!

rows.label: qst701005_msg0008
rows.name:
Haha! I can't think of anything worse,
to be perfectly honest.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0009
rows.name:
If someone suggested a contest like
that, there'd be an Adel-shaped
hole in the door before you could blink.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0010
rows.name:
OK, so it's not that. What's this all
about, then?

rows.label: qst701005_msg0011
rows.name:
That was an amusing diversion, but
you mentioned cutting to the chase?

rows.label: qst701005_msg0012
rows.name:
My dad said that? God's sakes,
I'm so sorry about him. He's a toughie.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0013
rows.name:
No need to apologize - he's a
straight talker and I respect that.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0014
rows.name:
The handyman Dio seemed to think
that worrying about his only daughter
has Zain's hackles up a bit...

rows.label: qst701005_msg0015
rows.name:
Oh. You think so? I can't imagine that
would make dad so angry, though.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0016
rows.name:
Back when Kaede named the Waytree
after him, you used the words "grumpy
and stubborn", right?

rows.label: qst701005_msg0017
rows.name:
Yeah...I did say that.
But that stuff he said to you was a bit
beyond "grumpy".

rows.label: qst701005_msg0018
rows.name:
Something to do with that Blade
Metsu setting his sights on the capital,
perhaps?

rows.label: qst701005_msg0019
rows.name:
Oh, Kaede, what should I do? I'm still
on my journey of self-improvement...

rows.label: qst701005_msg0020
rows.name: You're going to go home, right?

rows.label: qst701005_msg0021
rows.name:
I see no reason not to go back
and help these people.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0022
rows.name:
Yeah. Thanks, Kaede-chan, you're the best!
You always know what to do.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0023
rows.name:
OK, then! I guess I'll see you back at
the capital!
